<br>
It doesn't sound like anyone thinks they are better off than before, so unless someone has really good data, I think we can rule out the rumor that avoidance was increased.<br>
<br>
Sounds like this was a straight nerf to mitigation, and that very uber gear can overcome the nerf. Monks with 1500 AC are saying that they don't notice a difference.<br>
<br>
So there must be a cutoff point somewhere. Lets hear from people, list level and AC and how the nerf is hurting you. <p><br>--
